definitions.text:
@nỗi mình
- One's personal lot, one's personal plight.
="Nghĩ mình mình lại thêm thương nỗi mình " (Nguyễn Du)+The more one thought of one's personal plight, the more grieved one was

@nỗi niềm
- cũng nói nỗi riêng Innermost feelings, confidence.
="Nỗi niềm tâm sự hỏi ai " (Nguyễn Du)+Whom can one consult on one's innermost feelings?

@nỗi
- Feeling
=Nỗi đau khổ+A feeling of sadness
